Site.Name: Buckman Well Field, Southern Espanola Basin, NM, USA
Site.Comments: This data was acquired as part of the SAGE program in summer 2012 using the EMI MT24LF broadband instruments. Data consists of four stations on the Caja del Rio Plateau on Santa Fe Forest land.Multi-station remote- reference processing was used to improve the estimated transfer functions.
